\item Band-gaps are not the only feature of a successful semiconductor.
\vspace{0.5cm}

\item What other properties do strained or doped GNRs posses?
\vspace{0.3cm}
\begin{itemize}
\item Electron transport calculations.
\end{itemize}


\end{itemize}

\end{frame}


